US spelling of [[disk]]

====Computing Usage====
In International English, ''disc'' is the correct spelling for optical ''discs''. If the medium is magnetic, the variant ''[[disk]]'' is used.

#Optical medium
#*Gazza bought some blank '''[[compact disc]]s''' yesterday
#Magnetic medium
#*Jim still uses '''[[floppy disk]]s''' from 1979

US spelling dictates that '''[[disc]]''' should be used for all mediums of data storing disks/discs.

